Recommended Monitoring Stack for OWASP Juice Shop

Because the Juice Shop application is built on Node.js/Express, the industry standard for monitoring this environment is the kube-prometheus-stack (Prometheus + Grafana).

    Prometheus Operator: Automatically discovers cluster components and scrapes application targets via custom ServiceMonitor definitions.

    Node Exporter: Installed on the worker nodes to track raw physical device consumption (CPU, Memory, and Disk I/O across your 80G partition).

    Nginx Ingress Prometheus Metrics: Captures critical edge data (HTTP Request Volume, Request Latency, and 4xx/5xx error rates) to detect malicious scanning attempts against the web app.

    Grafana Dashboards: Aggregates metrics into real-time operational views to analyze active user connections, payload throughput, and pod cluster resource limitations.
